.youtube.com/embed/Ju86mknumYM","bgimage":null,"bgxposition":"50","bgyposition":"50","bgsize":"cover","overlay":null,"overlaycolor":"#ffffff","overlayopacity":"50","bgcolor":"#eeeeee","color2":"#c0c0c0","blockwidth":"default","fullheight":"false","toppadding":"30","bottompadding":"30","contentname":null,"previous":"/content/themecleanflex/pages/library/breadcrumb/sample","next":"/content/themecleanflex/pages/library/code/sample-blank","component":"themecleanflex-components-pager","path":"/jcr:content/pager0"},{"experiences":null,"children":[{"experiences":null,"text":"<h1 id=\"code\">Code</h1> <p>This component renders the text as <code>&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-{{language}} {{classes}}&quot;&gt;{{text}}&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;</code></p> <p>If the base template includes prism.js it will be used to generate the markup of the code. </p> <h2 id=\"configuring-prism\">Configuring Prism</h2> <p><em>Please note: Using Prism will impact your site&#39;s accessibility and mobile performance score. This is not an issue with Peregrine, rather a consequence of using Prism.</em></p> <p>If you wish to use <a href=\"Prism\">https://prismjs.com/</a> with the code component, perform the following steps:</p> <ol> <li><p>Visit the Prism <a href=\"https://prismjs.com/download.html\">download page</a> and download <code>prism.js</code> and <code>prism.css</code> with the options that you need.</p> </li> <li><p>Upload <code>prism.js</code> and <code>prism.css</code> to <code>Assets</code>. It is recommended that you create folders for <code>/content/_tenant_/assets/css/</code> and <code>/content/_tenant_/assets/js/</code> first, then upload <code>prism.js</code> and <code>prism.css</code> to their respective folders.</p> </li> <li><p>Click on the <code>Template</code> tile from the home screen, then click on the page icon for your tenant.  </p> </li> <li><p>Click <code>page start</code>.</p> </li> <li><p>(optional) If you enabled the <code>Copy to Clipboard button</code> when you downloaded Prism, add <code>https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/clipboard.js/2.0.4/clipboard.min.js</code> to <code>Site JS Files</code>.</p> </li> <li><p>Add <code>/content/_tenant_/assets/js/prism.js</code> to <code>Site JS Files</code>.</p> </li> <li><p>Add <code>/content/_tenant_/assets/css/prism.css</code> to <code>Site CSS Files</code>.</p> </li> <li><p>Navigate to your site, edit a page and place a <em>Code</em> component on the page. Enter your language without the <code>language-</code> prefix (e.g., ruby, script, java, etc). You can add additional classes to the <code>classes</code> property. For example, adding <code>line-numbers</code> will enable line numbers if you included the line number plugin when you downloaded Prism.</p> </li> </ol> <h2 id=\"pending-features--issues\">Pending Features &amp; Issues</h2> <ul> <li>Add support for defining Prism data attributes</li> <li>Update the code component to be less plugin dependent</li> </ul> ","showmedia":null,"mediatype":null,"imagesrc":"","videosrc":"","mediatitle":null,"mediawidth":"50","mediaposition":"before","anchorname":null,"extraclasses":null,"htmlelement":"banner","colorscheme":"","custombackground":"true","backgroundtype":"color","bgvideo":"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Ju86mknumYM","bgimage":null,"bgxposition":"50","bgyposition":"50","bgsize":"cover","overlay":null,"overlaycolor":"#ffffff","overlayopacity":"50","bgcolor":"#eeeeee","color2":"#c0c0c0","blockwidth":"default","fullheight":"false","toppadding":"25","bottompadding":"25","contentname":null,"component":"themecleanflex-components-richtext","path":"/jcr:content/container6/intro1"},{"experiences":null,"text":"<h2>Code (Text Components)</h2>","showmedia":null,"mediatype":null,"imagesrc":"","videosrc":"","mediatitle":null,"mediawidth":"50","mediaposition":"before","anchorname":null,"extraclasses":null,"htmlelement":"section","colorscheme":"","custombackground":"true","backgroundtype":"color","bgvideo":"https://www.youtube.com/embe